一:ruby on rails 环境搭建
 
1:安装ruby
  1: tar xzvf ruby.tar.gz
     cd ruby-1.8.5
     ./configure –prefix=/usr/local/ruby
     make && make install
  
2:安装gem
   tar xzvf rubygems.tgz
   cd rubygems-0.9.0/
   ruby setup.rb 

3:安装 rails

   gem install rails –y

以上三步创建一个ruby On Rails 开发环境，如有错误异常请参考博客http://blog.csdn.net/liaoceo/article/details/8942482


